{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"main_12_level_main_12-01_end","storyGroup":"main_12","storySort":118,"storyDependence":"main_12_level_main_12-01_end","storyCanShow":0,"storyCode":"12-2","storyName":"静候驾临","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"诺伯特区中的格拉斯哥帮在新首领卡铎尔的领导下艰难保全着他们的拳馆。被监视的戈尔丁只能委托茉莉去警告自救军及时转移。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"obt/main/level_main_12-01_end","avgTag":"行动后","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"main_12-01","minState":"PASS","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":1,"next":3,"characters":["贝尔德","卡铎尔","胆怯的市民","戴菲恩","戈尔丁","茉莉","阿米娅","阿斯卡纶"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"dialog","id":2},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":3},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/8a/Avg_bg_37_g1_glasgowboxinggym.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":5},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":6},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$m_dia_street_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta3_181101/m_dia_street_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":7,"musicid":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":8},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":9},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_177","focus":"r","duration":"1","id":10},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_863_1#5$1","focus":"l","duration":"1","id":11},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":12},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_177","focus":"l","id":13},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贝尔德","text":"行了，这里暂且安全。","id":14,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/10/Avg_avg_npc_863_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","duration":"0","id":15},{"type":"dialog","id":16},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_863_1#1$1","focus":"m","duration":"0.2","id":17},{"type":"delay","time":"0.2","id":18},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贝尔德","text":"卡铎尔，外面还是一团糟。我们确实已经不在伦蒂尼姆了，老卸货塔的塔顶应该能看到地块外的情况，但我接近不了，那在封锁区外。","id":19,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/31/Avg_avg_npc_863_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贝尔德","text":"我猜就算看到了，也没什么意义，萨卡兹看得很严，他们的人数......相当多。","id":20,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/31/Avg_avg_npc_863_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":21},{"type":"charslot","id":22},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#5$1","focus":"m","duration":"1","id":23},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":24},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"......我知道了。","id":25,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/48/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#12$1","focus":"m","id":26},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"这人怎么回事？","id":27,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/82/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":28},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_862_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":29},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_863_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":30},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贝尔德","text":"哼，想找萨卡兹谈条件。","id":31,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/31/Avg_avg_npc_863_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_862_1#12$1","focus":"l","id":32},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"结果呢？","id":33,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/82/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_863_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":34},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贝尔德","text":"自己看。","id":35,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/31/Avg_avg_npc_863_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":36},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":37},{"type":"charslot","id":38},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/8a/Avg_bg_37_g1_glasgowboxinggym.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":39},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_clothmovement","id":40},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":41},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_863_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":42},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贝尔德","text":"包扎好了，我只能做到这个程度了。","id":43,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/10/Avg_avg_npc_863_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_177","focus":"m","id":44},{"type":"dialogue","name":"胆怯的市民","text":"谢谢......谢谢你们。","id":45,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_npc_177.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"胆怯的市民","text":"天哪，为什么......到底发生了什么？","id":46,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_npc_177.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":47},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"还能发生什么？萨卡兹已经在伦蒂尼姆城里待了四年了。","id":48,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"你不会至今还以为他们是被可怜鬼卡文迪许请过来做客的吧？","id":49,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_177","focus":"m","id":50},{"type":"dialogue","name":"胆怯的市民","text":"可他们从来都没有......","id":51,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_npc_177.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":52},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"他们从来都没有什么？","id":53,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#11$1","focus":"m","id":54},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"看来，你一定是从不出门的贵族老爷，连早餐的瘤奶都需要仆人给你送到餐桌上。嘿，你怎么会沦落到我们诺伯特区来的。","id":55,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/fb/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_177","focus":"m","id":56},{"type":"dialogue","name":"胆怯的市民","text":"不不，我是个学者，只是经济上暂时有些麻烦......只要把手上的书稿写完，应该就能......","id":57,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_npc_177.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"胆怯的市民","text":"该死，我甚至没来得及把稿子带出书房！","id":58,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_npc_177.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":59},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"贝尔德，你真的很擅长找到些落魄鬼。","id":60,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/7e/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_177","focus":"m","id":61},{"type":"dialogue","name":"胆怯的市民","text":"请放尊重些，如果顺利，我很有可能是皇家科学院的下一个院士！","id":62,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_npc_177.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#11$1","focus":"m","id":63},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"“很有可能”，哼。","id":64,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/fb/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_177","focus":"m","id":65},{"type":"dialogue","name":"胆怯的市民","text":"我还是不明白，新闻里不总说......","id":66,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_npc_177.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":67},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"“一切太平”。你还想在广播里听到什么？“市民朋友们，很遗憾，伦蒂尼姆如今是个粪坑”？","id":68,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/c/c9/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"几年前派去各个报社和电视台的那些“特别指导专员”可不是白拿工资的。","id":69,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/c/c9/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"你没看过海布里区那些军工厂上现在飘着的是谁的旗帜？那奥克特里格区前几天的那场大火你总该记得吧。","id":70,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/c/c9/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_177","focus":"m","id":71},{"type":"dialogue","name":"胆怯的市民","text":"可，战争......城防军呢？大公爵们呢？他们不是应该已经在伦蒂尼姆周围保护我们了吗？","id":72,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_npc_177.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"胆怯的市民","text":"怎么就......萨卡兹们打不过大公爵的，对吧？那些魔族佬不过是一群缩在荒地上的野蛮人，可维多利亚是这片大地上最伟大的国家！","id":73,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_npc_177.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":74},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"谁告诉你的？一边在家里吃甜面包一边突然悟到的吗？","id":75,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/c/c9/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"反正我在被条子按在墙上搜身的时候，可从没感觉到过这一点。","id":76,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/c/c9/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#11$1","focus":"m","id":77},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"行了，“下个院士”，走吧，你不适合跟我们混在一起。","id":78,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/fb/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_177","focus":"m","id":79},{"type":"dialogue","name":"胆怯的市民","text":"可......可我该去哪儿？","id":80,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_npc_177.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"胆怯的市民","text":"我的公寓不在这片封锁区里，我忠诚的佣人也不知道去哪了......我在这儿谁也不认识。","id":81,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_npc_177.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":82},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"啧。","id":83,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/06/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_863_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":84},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贝尔德","text":"你会干什么？医疗，缝纫，维修，或者别的什么都好。","id":85,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/31/Avg_avg_npc_863_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_177","focus":"m","id":86},{"type":"dialogue","name":"胆怯的市民","text":"我，我的研究方向是纹章学......","id":87,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_npc_177.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":88},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"你们就没有研究把空气变成肉排的学问吗？","id":89,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/c/c9/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_177","focus":"m","id":90},{"type":"dialogue","name":"胆怯的市民","text":"这个......虽然不是我的学术方向，但可能是有一些难度......","id":91,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_npc_177.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#11$1","focus":"m","id":92},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"贝尔德，你不能再捡这些老爷们回来了，他甚至连玩笑都听不明白。","id":93,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/fb/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"我们的物资储备毕竟是有限的。","id":94,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/fb/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_863_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":95},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贝尔德","text":"唉......要不，去帮戴菲恩管仓库？","id":96,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/66/Avg_avg_npc_863_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":97},{"type":"charslot","id":98},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_runstop","volume":"1","id":99},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_866_1#3$1","duration":"0.7","id":100},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":101},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"贝尔德！你又想把麻烦事都甩给我！","id":102,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/83/Avg_avg_npc_866_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_863_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":103},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贝尔德","text":"可我总不能就看着他死在大街上。","id":104,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/31/Avg_avg_npc_863_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贝尔德","text":"在这种时刻，我们更需要团结。多个人总是多份力量。","id":105,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/31/Avg_avg_npc_863_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_866_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":106},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"“团结”......唉。","id":107,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/67/Avg_avg_npc_866_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"议会和大公爵们该向你们学学这点，否则我们也不会沦落到今天。","id":108,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/67/Avg_avg_npc_866_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_863_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":109},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贝尔德","text":"他们怎么不团结？在吊死国王这件事上就团结得很呢。","id":110,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/17/Avg_avg_npc_863_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_866_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":111},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"那时......唉，算了。","id":112,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/67/Avg_avg_npc_866_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_866_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":113},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"但愿你能派上点用场，“下个院士”先生。","id":114,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_866_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_177","focus":"m","id":115},{"type":"dialogue","name":"胆怯的市民","text":"我一定尽力！不过，说起来......你们是？","id":116,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_npc_177.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#11$1","focus":"m","id":117},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"我们？","id":118,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/fb/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":119},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"好吧，欢迎来到“揍歪下巴”拳馆！","id":120,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":121},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"你也可以喊我们格拉斯哥帮。","id":122,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/7e/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":123},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":124},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":125},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":126},{"type":"charslot","id":127},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/f8/Avg_bg_32_g3_school_indoor.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":128},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":129},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$loneliness_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/static/m_avg/m_avg_loneliness_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":130,"musicid":1},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":131},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":132},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_penrustle","volume":"1","id":133},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":134},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":135},{"type":"subtitle","text":"海蒂，你还好吗？","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":136},{"type":"subtitle","text":"事实上，我并不知道你最近在哪里，自从开书店的亚当斯先生死后，我已经有些日子没能联系上你了。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":137},{"type":"subtitle","text":"我已经很久没有继续我们的工作了。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":138},{"type":"subtitle","text":"请原谅我，我亲爱的朋友，我从不会向你隐瞒什么。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":139},{"type":"subtitle","text":"但我确实十分......迷茫。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":140},{"type":"subtitle","id":141},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":142},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":143},{"type":"dialog","id":144},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_647_1#5$1","duration":"1","id":145},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":146},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_647_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":147},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"你曾告诉我，和平一定会再次到来......","id":148,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d1/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"但我没法再用虚假的希望欺骗自己，我没法再躲进房间中，假装我们所做的一切仍然有意义。","id":149,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d1/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_647_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":150},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"是的，或许我们可以试着用一种更加长远的眼光，“历史的维度”......","id":151,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"当然，和平会到来，和平终会到来。","id":152,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"而战争，也一定会更加残忍地击碎它。","id":153,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"我曾相信我们能赢，我依然恳求我们能赢。","id":154,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_647_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":155},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"但是，海蒂，如果我们所做的一切，最终只是些自我安慰和自我宽解......","id":156,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d1/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_647_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":157},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"不，不是如果。或许这已经是事实......","id":158,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/f5/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_647_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":159},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"这些书本，这几张课桌，这个摇摇欲坠的学校......怎么能对抗一个时代？","id":160,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_647_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":161},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"海蒂，我没办法......我几乎没办法继续坚持。","id":162,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d1/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"我该怎么办？","id":163,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d1/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":164},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_647_1#5$1","afrom":"1","ato":"0","duration":"0.2","id":165},{"type":"delay","time":"0.7","id":166},{"type":"charslot","id":167},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_647_1#1$1","duration":"0","id":168},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.6","id":169},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_657_1#8$1","duration":"1","id":170},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":171},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_657_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":172},{"type":"dialogue","name":"茉莉","text":"戈尔丁女士，您还好吗？","id":173,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_647_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":174},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"茉莉......你回来了。","id":175,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/62/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_657_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":176},{"type":"dialogue","name":"茉莉","text":"您在写信吗？","id":177,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_647_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":178},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"不，这些什么也不是。","id":179,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/62/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_647_1#7$1","focus":"l","id":180},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"我只是......突然想起了几本以前看过的小说。","id":181,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"主角往往是风流倜傥的军官，穿着得体的军服，叼着烟斗奔赴前线。","id":182,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"但作者永远都不会告诉我们，到底是哪一片战场，战壕里的气味又是怎样。","id":183,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"恋慕着主人公的先生或者小姐们聚在一起，吃着精致的茶点，怀着一颗惴惴不安的心——","id":184,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_647_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":185},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"当然，我们都知道，这只是些文学技巧，最终的结局总是团圆。","id":186,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/62/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"稍有追求的作者会试图营造一种被这里的评论家们称作“深刻”的氛围。","id":187,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/62/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"故事中会点缀着一些可控的死亡，往往是主人公的战友，他们为了掩护英雄倒在了前线的壕沟里。","id":188,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/62/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"最终，那些凶残的敌人会被主人公手刃，正义与道德再一次得到彰显。","id":189,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/62/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"在战友哀伤的葬礼上，代表荣耀的花瓣洒满棺椁，人群肃穆，献上总结他们伟大事业的悼词。","id":190,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/62/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"此刻是绝佳的煽情点，主人公们会手握着手，擦去泪花，坚定地望向天边的朝阳——","id":191,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/62/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_647_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":192},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"他们会说，希望终会来临，一切牺牲都有意义。","id":193,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/f5/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"好了，作者可以在这里停下了，真正美好的未来就交给读者们去想象吧，最后的庄严感足够让他们满足了。","id":194,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/f5/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_657_1#4$1","focus":"r","id":195},{"type":"dialogue","name":"茉莉","text":"您居然还读过这样的小说。","id":196,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/29/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_647_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":197},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"那是很多年前了，谁没有经历过那样的年纪呢。","id":198,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"在我还是个少女的时候，一度十分迷恋这些书......我并不对主人公们抱有太多感情，但那些死亡确实让我迷恋。","id":199,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_647_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":200},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"我偶尔会想象自己是那位为事业献上生命的英雄，人们含着眼泪，夸赞我所创造的时代，或者，最起码，称颂我的牺牲......","id":201,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/62/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_647_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":202},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"哈，很幼稚。","id":203,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_647_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":204},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"再后来，我自以为自己已经足够清醒，足够看穿这些裹着糖霜的幻想。","id":205,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/62/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_647_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":206},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"但我开始发现......我与当年，或许没有本质上的不同。","id":207,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d1/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_657_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":208},{"type":"dialogue","name":"茉莉","text":"别这么说，您以前和孩子们说过，死亡是个严肃的话题。","id":209,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/de/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_647_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":210},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"......哈，是吗？我不记得了。","id":211,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"大概只是些我习以为常的老套说教吧。","id":212,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"今天的采购顺利吗？","id":213,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_657_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":214},{"type":"dialogue","name":"茉莉","text":"还好，街上的情况并没有很糟，商店里的东西也没有涨价。只是城防军好像比以往多了些。萨卡兹士兵们......也不再遮遮掩掩。","id":215,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_657_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":216},{"type":"dialogue","name":"茉莉","text":"不过，大家都在假装什么都没有发生。除了......原本是诺伯特区的地方，如今只剩下周围区块延伸过来的支撑骨架。","id":217,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/de/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_647_1#10$1","focus":"l","id":218},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"......那些地方呢？","id":219,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/c/c0/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_647_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":220},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"茉莉，我要再次向你道歉，我不该把你牵扯进这些事里，只是......莱托已经盯上了我，每次我出门都有几个不怀好意的人跟着。","id":221,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d1/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_647_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":222},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"我只能赌一把，赌你还不在他们的监视名单上。","id":223,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/62/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_657_1#7$1","focus":"r","id":224},{"type":"dialogue","name":"茉莉","text":"不，我很高兴能为伦蒂尼姆的大家出一份力。","id":225,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ec/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_657_1#6$1","focus":"r","id":226},{"type":"dialogue","name":"茉莉","text":"只是，您所说的几个地点，现在都冷冷清清的，那些接头暗号我都用了，也没有人回应。","id":227,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/fc/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_657_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":228},{"type":"dialogue","name":"茉莉","text":"也许......也许他们已经放弃了？","id":229,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_647_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":230},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"不，他们比我坚强得多。","id":231,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/62/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1.5","id":232},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_657_1#6$1","focus":"r","id":233},{"type":"dialogue","name":"茉莉","text":"不过我发现了一封信，应该是留给您的，我没拆。","id":234,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/fc/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":235},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_657_1#6$1","focus":"all","id":236},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_paper1","volume":"1","id":237},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":238},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$nervous_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_nervous_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":239,"musicid":2},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_647_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":240},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"这是......不，这不是他们的笔迹。","id":241,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/7d/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"......信里详细写了自救军情报交换站的几乎全部信息。","id":242,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/7d/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_657_1#4$1","focus":"r","id":243},{"type":"dialogue","name":"茉莉","text":"您说什么？！可是，怎么会......","id":244,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/29/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_647_1#6$1","focus":"l","id":245},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"这是一次威胁。","id":246,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"他们......对我们掌握得很彻底。","id":247,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_657_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":248},{"type":"dialogue","name":"茉莉","text":"那......戈尔丁女士，那我们该怎么办？！","id":249,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/de/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_647_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":250},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"......","id":251,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/f5/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_647_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":252},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"茉莉，我会再给你一份地点列表。","id":253,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/62/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"我并没有直接去过这些据点，但我分析过情报的流向，他们......应该就在那里。","id":254,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/62/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"我不该这么冒险，这违反了工作守则，但是......","id":255,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/62/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_657_1#6$1","focus":"r","id":256},{"type":"dialogue","name":"茉莉","text":"这消息对自救军很重要，对吧？","id":257,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/fc/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_647_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":258},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"这关乎很多人的性命。","id":259,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/62/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_657_1#6$1","focus":"r","id":260},{"type":"dialogue","name":"茉莉","text":"那我们就应该去做。","id":261,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/fc/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":262},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_647_1#6$1","focus":"all","id":263},{"type":"delay","time":"0.2","id":264},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":265},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_647_1#6$1","posfrom":"0,0","posto":"-50,0","afrom":"1","ato":"1","duration":"2","id":266},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":267},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_647_1#6$1","focus":"l","id":268},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"......茉莉，像我教你的那样，留意所有可能的尾随者，不论跟着你的人是不是萨卡兹，都不要掉以轻心。","id":269,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"在那里找到一个叫克洛维希娅的女孩，或者任何能联系到克洛维希娅的人，告诉他们，整个情报网泄露了，他们需要马上转移！","id":270,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_657_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":271},{"type":"dialogue","name":"茉莉","text":"戈尔丁女士，您要去哪？","id":272,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_647_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":273},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"莱托的办公室。","id":274,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/62/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"......我会尽量为你们争取时间。","id":275,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/62/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_657_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":276},{"type":"dialogue","name":"茉莉","text":"可是——","id":277,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/de/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_647_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":278},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"放心吧，我不会有事的，我......","id":279,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"但愿我比自己想象的要强大。","id":280,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":281},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":282},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":283},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":284},{"type":"charslot","id":285},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b7/Avg_bg_27_g6_hideout.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":286},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":287},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$darkness02_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_darkness02_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":288,"musicid":3},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":289},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":290},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#2$1","duration":"0.7","id":291},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":292},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":293},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"......","id":294,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/16/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"博士，我做了一个梦。","id":295,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/16/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我梦见......阴云笼罩了这座城市，沾血的萨卡兹旗帜在每一座建筑上空飘扬，而城外......源石簇长满了目力所及的每一个角落。","id":296,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/16/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我梦见锈色的王座在大地上矗立，人们跪拜，流下黑色的眼泪；我梦见王座上的人轻挥手臂，呐喊声便刺破了整片天空。","id":297,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/16/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#11$1","focus":"m","id":298},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"然而，王座的阴影里，瑟缩的人们悄悄抬起头......","id":299,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/48/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我能感受到他们的感情......","id":300,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/48/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我不知该怎么描述......那么驳杂，那么压抑......","id":301,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/48/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我只能辨别出浮在最表面的那些，那种痛苦......","id":302,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/48/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#18$1","focus":"m","id":303},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"......还有仇恨。","id":304,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-18$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"......","id":305,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-18$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"王座上的人......是谁？","id":306,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-18$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"......这是萨卡兹众魂预见的未来吗？还是，一位魔王的使命？","id":307,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-18$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":308},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"特蕾西娅小姐是不是也做过这个梦？会不会......这就是她现在所期盼的场景？","id":309,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/16/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":310},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":311},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#17$1","focus":"m","id":312},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"不，不会的。","id":313,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/2d/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-17$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"博士，这个梦......它什么都不是，对吗？","id":314,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/2d/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-17$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":315},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#17$1","focus":"none","id":316},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"318","text":"你最近太累了。"},"2":{"id":"318","text":"梦只是梦而已。"}},"values":[],"id":317},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":318,"end":322},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#21$1","focus":"m","id":319},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"......谢谢你，博士。","id":320,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ac/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-21$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#17$1","focus":"m","id":321},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"是啊，那只是一个梦......而已......","id":322,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/2d/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-17$1.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":323},{"type":"charslot","id":324},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.6","id":325},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_395_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":326},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":327},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"阿米娅，博士。","id":328,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/52/Avg_avg_npc_395_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#19$1","focus":"m","id":329},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"凯尔希医生好些了吗？","id":330,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/e5/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-19$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_395_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":331},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"说不上好，她的身体......本就称得上瘦弱。伤口很深。","id":332,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/f7/Avg_avg_npc_395_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"闪灵已经尝试了几种办法，但效果都很有限，她还没有苏醒。","id":333,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/f7/Avg_avg_npc_395_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"Mon3tr看起来在缓慢地自我修复，我们同样不知道它能恢复到什么程度，乃至它是否能真正恢复。","id":334,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/f7/Avg_avg_npc_395_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#18$1","focus":"m","id":335},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我......","id":336,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-18$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"......博士，城防军指挥塔上，如果我能......","id":337,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-18$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":338},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#18$1","focus":"none","id":339},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"341","text":"每个人都已经做到了最好。"},"2":{"id":"341","text":"谁也不会想到特雷西斯会出现在那里。"}},"values":[],"id":340},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":341,"end":351},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":342},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"凯尔希医生......","id":343,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/16/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我从没想过，有一天凯尔希医生居然会伤得这么重......","id":344,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/16/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"她总是会游刃有余地处理好一切问题，她总能给我们提供最恰当的建议。","id":345,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/16/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#11$1","focus":"m","id":346},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"她可是凯尔希医生，我甚至从没看到过她疲惫的样子！","id":347,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/48/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"可是，现在......","id":348,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/48/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":349},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"......","id":350,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/16/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"博士......","id":351,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/16/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-2$1.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":352},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#2$1","focus":"none","id":353},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"355","text":"（牵住阿米娅的手）"}},"values":[],"id":354},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":355,"end":364},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#17$1","focus":"m","id":356},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我知道，我会担负起我的责任。罗德岛在这里的使命还远没有结束。","id":357,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/2d/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-17$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"但现在......我想再去看看凯尔希医生，可以吗？","id":358,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/2d/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-17$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"哪怕是在她的床边坐一会儿也好。","id":359,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/2d/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-17$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_395_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":360},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"两位，相比于陪护重伤员，你们现在有更重要的工作要做。","id":361,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/52/Avg_avg_npc_395_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"可露希尔让我告诉你们，城防军指挥塔上的那些数据已经解析完毕。","id":362,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/52/Avg_avg_npc_395_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"克洛维希娅正在召集一场会议。","id":363,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/52/Avg_avg_npc_395_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"我们需要重新评估伦蒂尼姆的局势了。","id":364,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/52/Avg_avg_npc_395_1-1$1.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":365},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_395_1#1$1","focus":"none","id":366},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"368","text":"战争爆发了。"},"2":{"id":"368","text":"我们的初步计划失败了。"}},"values":[],"id":367},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":368,"end":370},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_395_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":369},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"那么，告诉我们，下一步应该怎么做。","id":370,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/52/Avg_avg_npc_395_1-1$1.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":371},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":372},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":373},{"type":"charslot","id":374},{"type":"image","id":375}],"characters":["贝尔德","卡铎尔","胆怯的市民","戴菲恩","戈尔丁","茉莉","阿米娅","阿斯卡纶"]}